To build the icinga2 container, run:

# docker build -t waja/debian_icinga2:wheezy .

To start the icinga2 container, run:

# docker run -i -rm -t waja/debian_icinga2:wheezy

This image has a conf.d directory which is intended to get exported into /etc/icinga2/conf.d/docker/ inside the container:

# docker run -i -rm -t waja/debian_icinga2:wheezy -v $(pwd)/conf.d:/etc/icinga2/conf.d/docker/ 

A similar project can be found at https://github.com/jjethwa/icinga2
